</li><li class="sense" sensenum="2" htag="li" hclass="sense" id="annieoakley_sng_1"><span class="sensetop" hclass="sensetop" htag="span"><span class="labels" htag="span" hclass="labels">(North American English, informal)</span></span> <span class="def" htag="span" hclass="def">a free ticket or pass, for example for a theatre performance. It is called this because it has holes in it (so that it cannot be used again) and looks like one of the cards shot by <span class="dh">Annie Oakley</span> as part of her act.</span>      </li></ol><div class="pron-link">Check pronunciation:
